OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSir Philip Pullman resigns 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fas Society of Authors      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpresident after book row   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Author Sir Philip Pullman has resigned 
OL,6, as president of the Society of Authors 
OL,7, in the wake of a controversy over his  
OL,8, support for an author who was accused  
OL,9, of racial and ableist stereotyping.    
OL,11,FLast year, the His Dark Materials      
OL,12,Fwriter backed Kate Clanchy after her   
OL,13,Fmemoir attracted criticism.            
OL,15,FThe society, a trade union for authors,
OL,16,Fdistanced itself from his comments.    
OL,18,FHe has now said he "would not be free  
OL,19,Fto express my personal opinions as long
OL,20,Fas I remained president".              
